Replace the scriptRegistry.json file with a fresh download from jira.
To download the file, make a POST request to https://baseURL/rest/scriptrunner/latest/canned/com.onresolve.scriptrunner.canned.jira.admin.ScriptRegistry

toHtmlTable.groovy converts JSON to HTML
This results in 2 files: workflows.html and others.html
It is better to open it locally, not from the IDE

search.groovy searches for text in JSON and generates an HTML table with the results.
